## ğŸ§© Adding Widgets

Streamlit provides intuitive UI widgets:

```python
st.slider("Select a number", 0, 100, 50)
st.checkbox("Enable feature")
st.radio("Choose an option", ["A", "B", "C"])
st.selectbox("Pick a fruit", ["Apple", "Banana", "Cherry"])
